Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sleep in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left your mother there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next morning, you were told...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that your mother froze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the time, you thought to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only left her there because she asked you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only let those who wanted to die, die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't wrong. You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set them free from the misery of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva wants to die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then, the devil arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed by making sure not to look at the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't look...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must not look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recited that to myself, like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva wants to die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please kill me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leave me here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,won't be a part of the devil's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because nobody...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wants to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:10.46,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(378,0)\pos(359,336)}The Man Who Knew Too Much
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva isn't here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you send her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NLosing your life for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:03.43,Name,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(369,0)\pos(353,381)}5 Minutes Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their car just stopped outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stole a maid's uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that on and escape through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave together...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like asking to be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be killed if you don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm by myself, I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the place written in the note on the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tenma's hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you at Frankfurt Central Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to Tenma's place is the only way you'll be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's what you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to give me orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything reckless that'll get you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no obligation to go that far for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no obligation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no obligation to go that far for that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised I lived through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankfurt Central Station, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'm out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a suburb of Frankfurt...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}four people died in a gunfight at\Nthe Regen Motel in Sossenheim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is thought that the fight was an internal gang dispute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The police are now questioning the people staying\Nat the motel, to get a better picture...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robby...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that, Robby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the story of my fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robby...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we at Frankfurt Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done all the emergency treatment I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't do the rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Eva...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She... didn't come here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing about, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned... too many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Rose Mansion experiment is still going...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand... what I'm saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the devil got himself a disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is trying to create a dictator...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man with glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The survivor from the Red Rose Mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter... {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter... {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is trying to control the devil, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The devil is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The devil is more terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Jahreszeit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 606...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where the devil's disciple is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not... look at the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not play a part in the devil's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody... wants to... die...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Martin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... so fortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to look at the devil anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:11:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at Frankfurt Central Station...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she bought two tickets for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we could go as far as we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Eva waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect Eva for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to go to the station, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to wait there, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got plenty of time before the first train comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a guy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working at the station for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can you tell if someone will come or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a fortune teller.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the fact that you have someone\Nto wait for is a happy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether the person comes or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get the chance for something\Nlike that when you're my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess the person you're waiting for is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Martin is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he wasn't the one she was waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came to my place to give me\Nsome important information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the last of his strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still time before the first train comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you keep me company for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you don't want alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hated alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty worn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are, holding a funeral for Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a good person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did terrible things... to such a good person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made him wear the same suit and tie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I once gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the absolute worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even gave false testimony against you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that made you out to be guilty of a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why am I still alive and well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Martin protected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he protect a woman like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nobody wants to die."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Martin said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you were waiting for him at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That alone made him happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Munich...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of mine who's a psychological counselor is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, ask Dr. Reichwein to hide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll treat you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them that you're being targeted by\NThe Baby's organization in Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how you're being targeted by Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't kill anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was Johan's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should come to Munich, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw him at the party, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lose any more people like Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to bring this to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write a letter to Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll include all the information I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way you can help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is by going to Munich and telling them everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well to bring us and Johan together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:21:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard rumors that someone like him was in Frankfurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we asked you to help us identify him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me for interrupting you during your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An apartment on Haldecker Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An apartment on Haldecker Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can bring this to an end, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel Jahreszeit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 606...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where the devil's disciple is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who wants a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many different types of guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the biggest one you can give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beginner can't handle a big gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.58,0:22:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:31.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:44.44,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.40,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:23:01.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:25.94,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:34.36,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:36.82,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
